<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <script src="//c.hotread.com/wap/flexible-0.3.4.js"></script>
    <title>火星小说</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../styles/story-wap.min.css">
</head>

<body class="qr-body">
    <div class="wechat-pay" id="wechatPay">
        <div class="pay-back">
            <a href="./pay.html"><i class="icon-back"></i> 返回支付页面</a>
            <a href="./userCenter.html" class="success">支付完成</a>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p class="tips wechat-tips">长按图片识别二维码进行微信支付</p>
            <p class="tips browser-tips">长按图片保存，然后在“微信”中打开“扫一扫”，选择右上角“相册”中保存的支付二维码进行支付</p>
            <img src="http://c.hotread.com/assets/images/qrcode_wyw.jpg" alt="">
            <p class="tips">支付完成后点击上方【返回支付页面】查看支付结果</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script>
        ;(function () {
            if (/micromessenger/i.test(navigator.userAgent)) {
                document.getElementById('wechatPay').className = 'wechat-pay os-wechat';
            }
        })();
    </script>
</body>

</html>
